"히나","body":"흐아~ 지친다~\n1주일 동안 계속해서 레슨이라니 그런 소리는 없었잖아~!\n진짜로 연주할 것도 아닌데~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"band4-002-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"(유닛이 결성되고부터 매일 레슨이야.\n하지만 실제로 연주하진 않을 거라서 그런가……?\n스태프도 전력을 다해 가르친다는 느낌이 들지 않아.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"odoodo02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"band4-002-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"……수고하셨습니다!\n미안해. 다른 일정이 있어서 참가 못 했네요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"band4-002-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":0}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"(이 1주 동안 멤버들끼리 친해지기는 했지만\n치사토 짱에게는 아직 거리감이 느껴진다. 레슨에 의미가 없다고\n생각해서 그런지, 거의 참가조차 하지 않아.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":0,"voiceId":"band4-002-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"괜찮을까…… 우리.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"band4-002-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"흠~ 역시 마야 씨는 악기를 잘 아시네요!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"band4-002-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"아닙니다, 별말씀을요.\n설마 제 이야기를 이렇게 잘 들어주는 사람이 있을 줄이야……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"band4-002-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"아니 마야 짱. 마야 짱의 이야기 정말 재밌는데~?\n특히 전에 했던 전압 이야기 같은 거 꽤나 흥미진진했어~!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"band4-002-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"오홋!? 전압 이야기 흥미로우셨습니까?\n우와아! 기쁨다~!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"talk01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"band4-002-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"……그런데\n마야 짱이 대타 드러머라니 아깝다.\n이렇게 재미난 애인데.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"band4-002-049","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"드럼 치실 분은 아직 찾지 못한 걸까요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"band4-002-050","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"곧 있으면 1주일 지나네.\n계속해서 마야 짱한테 부탁할 수도 없는 노릇인데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"band4-002-051","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"만약 드럼을 찾을 수 없다면……\n우리 데뷔 이벤트는 못 하게 되나요?\n그러면 우리는 어떻게 되는 걸까요……?","tention":0,"lip